highlights.text: “That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 14 weeks straight.
Drake has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Passionfruit” is the highest at #2.
“At My Best (feat. Hailee Steinfeld)” by Machine Gun Kelly and Hailee Steinfeld is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 45 spots at #130.
“The Heart Part 4” by Kendrick Lamar is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #41.
